author: cbs8
title: Baton Rouge girl found bound, gagged in drainage canal
text:
BATON ROUGE, La. (AP) - A 15-year-old girl was found bound and gagged in a Baton Rouge drainage canal.
Baton Rouge Police spokesman Cpl. L'Jean McKneely tells The Advocate ( http://bit.ly/1NSJj4J ) a passer-by noticed the teenager in a ditch Tuesday at about 1:19 p.m.
McKneely says the girl told investigators she was attacked by three males. He could not confirm whether she was sexually assaulted.
The teenager, of Baton Rouge, was reported missing as a runaway Monday night. He says she is being treated at an area hospital.
Information from: The Advocate, http://theadvocate.com
